# 📊 Student Performance Analytics System

## Description

This project was developed as my **CBSE Class 12 Informatics Practices Final Practical Project**. It is a Python-based Student Performance Analytics System that analyzes and visualizes students' academic performance using data analysis and visualization techniques.

## Features
- Student marks analysis
- Graph generation
- Performance comparison

## Technologies Used
- Python
- NumPy
- Pandas
- Matplotlib

## How to Run
1. Clone the repository
2. Install requirements
3. Run Project.py

